{"parentUuid":"641118df-35e3-421a-94a3-fcd5bb7eb44d","isSidechain":false,"message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01BLFEUvfujhPmBzi32gZwW5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Go 開発で自動再起動する方法はいくつかあります：\n\n## 推奨: **air** を使う\n最も一般的で、Go コミュニティで広く使われています。\n\n```bash\n# インストール\ngo install github.com/cosmtrek/air@latest\n\n# プロジェクトで初期化\nair init\n\n# 実行\nair\n```\n\n`.air.toml` で以下のように設定できます：\n```toml\nroot = \".\"\ntestdata_dir = \"testdata\"\ntmp_dir = \"tmp\"\n\n[build]\n  cmd = \"go build -o ./tmp/main ./apps/api\"\n  bin = \"tmp/main\"\n  full_bin = \"\"\n  include_ext = [\"go\", \"tpl\", \"tmpl\", \"html\"]\n  exclude_dir = [\"assets\", \"tmp\", \"vendor\", \"testdata\"]\n  include_dir = []\n  delay = 1000\n  stop_on_error = true\n  log = \"build-errors.log\"\n  poll = false\n  poll_interval = 0\n\n[color]\n  main = \"magenta\"\n  watcher = \"cyan\"\n  build = \"yellow\"\n  yellow = \"\"\n```\n\n## 他の選択肢\n- **modd** - 複数コマンド同時実行も可能\n- **fswatch** + シェルスクリプト - よりカスタマイズ可能\n\nこのプロジェクトで **air** を採用したければ、セットアップまで手伝えます。必要ですか？"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":30582,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":726,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":30582,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CZY2e3AHnbmU2JBc3rAZ7","type":"assistant","uuid":"85d7220b-30d4-4ace-b158-b982481b34e9","timestamp":"2026-03-29T20:48:40.619Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"cli","cwd":"/Users/haru/ghq/github.com/harusame0616/ijuku","sessionId":"bb356a38-004e-4e78-b40d-730826678f38","version":"2.1.84","gitBranch":"enrollment"}
